%I A394095 #14 Jun 10 2026 16:33:37
%S A394095 1,2,7,61,2271,600408,1556743050
%N A394095 Number of 2-ary convexities on a set of n elements.
%C A394095 A convexity G on as set X is n-ary if its convex sets are precisely the sets A with the property that co(B) is a subset of A for each subset B with cardinality no more than n.
%D A394095 M. L. J. van de Vel, Theory of Convex Structures, North-Holland Mathematical Library, vol. 50, North-Holland, Amsterdam, 1993.
%H A394095 Daniil Naumikhin, <a href="https://github.com/SofaaSogo-oh/2gar-code">Enumeration of binary Convex Structures</a>, GitHub repository.
%H A394095 Daniil Naumikhin, <a href="/A394095/a394095.txt">List of convexities for a(3)=61</a>.
%e A394095 For n=2 the a(2)=7 binary convexities are following:
%e A394095   {{0, 1}, {}, {0}}
%e A394095   {{0, 1}, {0}}
%e A394095   {{0, 1}, {}, {1}}
%e A394095   {{0, 1}, {}}
%e A394095   {{0, 1}, {1}}
%e A394095   {{0, 1}, {}, {0}, {1}}
%e A394095   {{0, 1}}
%Y A394095 Cf. A326878, A000798.
%K A394095 nonn,hard,more
%O A394095 0,2
